{"tid":2138036,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"致讀環保既同學仔: WELLAB 匯力實驗室 睇落似水泡 實質係泥坑","createTime":"2020-08-03T10:37:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T08:28:00.000Z","uid":142115,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2ac59077629785e8dab9b74a914840655c647fe5","tid":2138036,"uid":142115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T10:37:32.000Z","msg":"黎緊又有好多讀環保既朋友會開始搵工, 又或者已經搵到, 呢間公司我翻過好短時間, 咩POST就唔講, 專請FG. 掛名就environmental consultant, 實質係9成時間出FIELD拎水辦泥辦度AIR NOISE WATER, LAB唔夠人仲要幫手做埋LAB. 當然如果你係鍾意出FIELD既可以一試, 但早排見佢已轉要簽一年死約, 之前就要約3個月死約. <br />\n<br />\n講真既, 學既野唔算多, 工作量亦唔算多, 但出FIELD果班其實同做地盤冇太大分別, 都係日搬夜搬. 工作時間唔定時要睇潮汐決定. 人工方面ENVIRONMENTAL黎講偏低. <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">簡單一句, 唔好做, 講完.</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n交代少少背景資料, 呢間公司同CINOTECH其實係有著千絲萬縷既關係, 甚至係同一棟大廈."},{"pid":"0ff1d0a67fdbc814e15fbc9ec626559e134f291b","tid":2138036,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T10:40:46.000Z","msg":"樓主冇得甩P<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10768877a998d568d7cee82c16809797f673f020","tid":2138036,"uid":23400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T10:55:55.000Z","msg":"Cinotech?"},{"pid":"7326732b80eb0a312cb9f2a461fa5ef8b7bf5959","tid":2138036,"uid":362827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T10:56:50.000Z","msg":"人工幾多"},{"pid":"7fe9a2dae7e71cb6f7d4b40da23d276d560427bb","tid":2138036,"uid":337927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T12:23:58.000Z","msg":"有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2886481f6ad02e98e327eeaf69c393fa8d39af4","tid":2138036,"uid":364489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T04:21:31.000Z","msg":"聽個fd講當時都係比個title 呃左入去 之後日日夜夜都係出海sampling 人又唔請多個 一個人每日都做幾單project既monitoring  重點真係學唔到嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebaa99c75d5f333e8f9bfa9107eeba9